				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Who are you, and why do you play in Molto Espressivo?<a name="56796"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 15 04 4:12 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Just to give the casual observer an idea of what kinds of people we have in the guild, I'd like our members to post here about themselves and their experiences in Molto Espressivo.  In particular:
<br />

<br />
1.  What was your EQ experience prior to joining Molto?
<br />

<br />
2.  Why did you join Molto?
<br />

<br />
3.  What are your favorite memories of Molto?
<br />

<br />
4.  What is your typical day in Molto like?
<br />

<br />
5.  Any other comments you would have about your time in Molto are welcome.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
