I started playing EQabout one month after release, started with a wizard DE on CT server, moved to Prexus when it came online as a newbie server, there i have a 59 cleric (my highest char), and a 55 bst.  Got a better job that takes up more of my time, good for real life but bad for EQ, suddenly i was in a situation where I would never again have the time to put into hours and hours long raids, and quests.  Was looking at never again gaining any of those nice NO DROP items..... then i remmbered that there are hardly any no drops on FV.
<br />
2. Why did you join Molto? 
<br />
I came to FV and chose to be a bard as I had not really played one before and it seeemed like a well rounded class able to fill many different rolls and functions.  LIttle did i know how darn great barding was, had i a clue before i would have beeen a bard these passed five years !!!
