<br />

<br />
I joined Molto because I wanted to fell a part of something.  I had never been in a guild before and after reading the Molto board I decided that I should give it a shot.
<br />
Also, I wanted something that would keep me interested.  I have had so many toons up to 25-30 but lost interest in them.  The idea of an all bard group sounded like something that could be alot of fun.
<br />
My final reason for joining was that after reading guide after guide, I knew that playing a bard was not going to be straight forward and easy... I was going to need help, and who better to help than people who have tons of experience in the class?
<br />

<br />
3. What are your favorite memories of Molto?
<br />

<br />
Well, I have only been in the guild for 3 weeks and am still very new.  During my time here, people have always had time to answer my questions and help me out.
<br />

<br />
