<br />

<br />
Get home from work - load up EQ - dive in a pond and practice wind and swimming while I have dinner and a shower - run around for a while until I settle on what zone I want - kill/die/run to zone etc <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
