3. What are your favorite memories of Molto? 
<br />

<br />
Only been here a couple days, will let you know when I get one.
<br />

<br />
4. What is your typical day in Molto like? 
<br />

<br />
Log in, level a little.  AFK practice my skills while I sleep.
<br />

<br />
5. Any other comments you would have about your time in Molto are welcome.
<br />

<br />
Everything seems great right now.  Having fun, everyone is helpful and positive.  Thus far exactly what I needed in the game.</span></td>
